						               													<description>Defiance of the Gods: The Rift is a board and card game that requires players to choose a side, Asgard or Olympus, use their deck to defend and attack strategic locations on the battleground with swords,  death rays, force shields, warships, the Hammer of Thor, the Head of Medusa and so much more&amp;hellip; Compete for control and destroy your opponent&amp;rsquo;s capital or ruler to win!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Defiance of the Gods has been designed so that players may build decks with the cards straight out the box. We have printed some cards less frequently, they are called Singularis cards and represent very powerful Gods, Generals, Weapons,  Treasures, Locations, Terrains, Tactics, etc. These cards can only be used one per deck and as such offer some of the most powerful effects in the game. In one box you will find 275 cards with multiples of staple cards included to help you build your deck and one of each Singularis card in the complete set for the specified edition.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
